Package: qnap-config-keeper
Version: 0.1.0
Depends: git
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: x86_64
Maintainer: GrEEV.com KG
Description: etckeeper-equivalent for QNAP QTS
 Track /etc/config, crontabs and QPKG list via Git.
 Local-only, no remote push. busybox ash compatible.
Source: https://github.com/KonradLanz/qnap-config-keeper
